{"tid":571821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[世紀難題]換顯示卡後喇叭冇聲","createTime":"2018-02-25T04:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T09:27:13.000Z","uid":36856,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"35b18f6e1e62dc34816f9b7efaf3ffce88f859db","tid":571821,"uid":36856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"裝咗張gtx 960落去之後就裝咗NVIDIA driver<br />\n然後喇叭就開始唔work(但detect到)<br />\n但我完全冇搞audio啲野<br />\n入右下角個播放設備到睇<br />\n已經係喇叭做預設(realtek audio)而且啲格仔有郁(當我play sound)<br />\n我套喇叭係用3.5mm<br />\n我轉用hdmi插落電視就有聲<br />\n所以hdmi audio work但3.5mm唔work<br />\n<br />\n已試：<br />\n1. uninstall and reinstall realtek + NVIDIA driver<br />\n2. 入安全模式uninstall and reinstall realtek + NVIDIA driver<br />\n3. 入NVIDIA關hdmi sound output<br />\n4. disable hdmi播放設備<br />\n5. 插front 3.5mm, 底板所有3.5mm<br />\n6. 入裝置管理員 disable/uninstall hdmi sound device<br />\n7. 拆走gpu行內顯(都冇聲)<br />\n<br />\ngoogle左成晚，見到好多人都有一樣嘅問題，但冇人解決到<br />\n<br />\n老母板 h81m<br />\nGPU msi gtx 960 100me<br />\n<br />\n相關案例：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tomsguide.com/answers/id-3178616/audio-jack-speakers-detect-sound-play.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomsguide.com%2Fanswers%2Fid-3178616%2Faudio-jack-speakers-detect-sound-play.html&d=NohmppOcrP8OYqKDbJf%2BYMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=483658de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tomsguide.com/answers/id-3178616/audio-jack-speakers-detect-sound-play.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/74670/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/74670/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/hardware/M.1435243911.A.33C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhardware%2FM.1435243911.A.33C.html&d=NohmppOcrP8OYqKDbJf%2BYMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=18545b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/hardware/M.1435243911.A.33C.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcdvd.com.tw//showthread.php?t=1009271\" data-sr-url